  <main style="max-width:700px; margin:auto; padding:1rem;">
    <img src="../images/pasta.jpg" alt="Creamy Pasta" style="width:100%; border-radius:8px;"/>
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>200g pasta</li>
      <li>1 cup cream</li>
      <li>2 cloves garlic</li>
      <li>Olive oil, salt, pepper</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Instructions</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Boil pasta until al dente.</li>
      <li>Sauté garlic in olive oil.</li>
      <li>Add cream, salt, pepper, and simmer.</li>
      <li>Toss pasta into the sauce and serve warm.</li>
    </ol>
  </main>

